Hurry up. The studio is waiting for you.

27
00:02:51,683 --> 00:02:52,683
Oh.

28
00:02:54,131 --> 00:02:55,559
By the way, Xiao Tan,

29
00:02:58,345 --> 00:02:59,516
don't casually take off your

30
00:02:59,541 --> 00:03:00,743
