31
00:03:02,361 --> 00:03:04,121
Close the door on your way out.

32
00:03:05,081 --> 00:03:06,081
Huh...

33
00:03:06,761 --> 00:03:08,246
Sorry, everyone.

34
00:03:08,450 --> 00:03:09,988
Got delayed by something.

35
